.Sh NAME
.Nm ihidev
.Nd HID over I2C support
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Cd "ihidev* at iic?"
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The
.Nm
driver provides support for Human Interface Devices (HID) on
Inter-Integrated Circuit (I2C) buses.
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr iic 4
.Sh HISTORY
The
.Nm
device driver first appeared in
.Ox 5.9 .
